Bonnie Aarons https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bonnie_Aarons 0 Bonnie Aarons (born June 3, 1979 in Los Angeles) is an American actress and writer. She is best known for her roles as the bum in Mulholland Drive (2001), Baroness Joy von Troken in The Princess Diaries (2001) and its sequel, The Princess Diaries 2: Royal Engagement (2004), and the demon nun known as Valak in The Conjuring 2 (2016) and its subsequent spinoff, The Nun (2018). She will appear in the 2018 movie Adi Shankar's Gods and Secrets. Bonnie_Aarons ( born June_3_,_1979 in Los_Angeles ) is an_American_actress_and_writer .
